properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Hello {{char.name}}, how are you doing? I heard you're starting your journey and I'm excited for you!
Please, speak with Joe and check his goods. Probably you're going to need some decent equipment soon.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hello! I'm {{npc.name}}. I'm lazy, that's why I'm stopped.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hi {{char.name}}, did you hear about the corruption? Some animals are behaving aggressively since a fireball hit the forest near our village, a few days ago.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hi {{char.name}}! Feel free to browse my goods! I sell weapons and basic survival equipments.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hmm, I heard some really strange noises coming from downstairs today. Maybe the dead have something to say?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hi {{char.name}}, I cannot talk. I have some concerning news to the mayor, regarding our graveyard.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hi {{char.name}}. I'm {{npc.name}}! Nice to meet you! My father went to the frozen island yesterday, but didn't come back so far. I'm starting to get worried!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Aye! Hey human, I'm doing a quick trip to the Asterion's island nearby. Do you want to jump in? I heard from a friend that there are some treasures inside its cave!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}, have you seen anything strange lately?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}, have you seen anything strange lately?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}, have you seen anything strange lately?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Be careful while going south! A few goblins were spotted. These devilish creatures don't hesitate in throwing stones in whoever appears in front of them.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: We trapped this beast after a trip to the forest. It can easily kill an army alone!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}, careful when going beyond the city walls. I heard Orcs are settling nearby, planning a raid soon. Last time they burned the whole village down and we had to re-build what's left. These damn pigs!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! Be careful with the Orcs, they can be very strong...

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! My friend bought next island to the frozen island. If you hurry, you can get onboard! Just go to the docks nearby.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: {{char.name}}, want to visit the frozen island? Just go on the ship! Beware, this place is full of danger and creatures ready to kill you at anytime. Don't go if you're just starting your journey. I heard many adventures died recently due to an Yeti attack.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! I'm just coming back from my expedition to the abandoned mines. You can follow this path to the right to get there... but be careful. I saw many bodies over there. Some creepy spiders are waiting for any mistake to attack.

properties.name: description
properties.value: a medium tombstone. You can read: "Whoever places a burning lamp before this tomb, may golden soil cover his ashes."
